      <p>RRS Realty Group is a <strong>referral and matching service</strong>. We connect homeowners and buyers in Southeast Wisconsin with independent, licensed third‑party real estate agents. <strong>RRS is not a licensed real estate brokerage and does not provide real estate brokerage services.</strong> All real estate services are performed by the independent licensed agents you are matched with, who are solely responsible for those services. We are not a party to, and are not responsible for, any agreement, transaction, advice, or relationship between you and a matched agent.</p>

