      <p>When you submit our form, you agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information. You authorize us to share the details you provide with one or more matched agents so they may contact you. You are responsible for the information you submit and for your interactions with any agent.</p>

      <h2>Consent to Be Contacted</h2>
      <p>By submitting our form, you consent to be contacted by RRS Realty Group and your matched agent(s) at the phone number and email address you provide — including by calls, prerecorded or autodialed messages, and text (SMS) messages — regarding your real estate inquiry. Consent is not a condition of any purchase. Message and data rates may apply, and message frequency varies. You may opt out of texts at any time by replying STOP, or opt out of other communications by contacting us. See our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>

